# Backend Monorepo

`__PM__` workspaces with `apps/*`.

```
backend/
├── package.json
└── apps/
    └── <name>/
```

## Scripts (run from `backend/`)

```bash
__PM__ install
__PM__ run dev      # runs every app's dev script
__PM__ run build
__PM__ run start
```

Or use the root CLI:

```bash
mx add:be <name>
mx run be <name> dev
mx run all dev
```
